'''Teebo Zirtran''' was one of the [[Zirtran brothers (disambiguation)|Zirtran Brothers]] who purchased the ''[[KV-29233-44B]]'' prototype and sold it on to the [[Geelan]] who soon converted it into the space station later to be known as [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

